<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 No other name
 But the Name of Jesus
 No other name
 But the Name of the Lord
 No other name
 But the Name of Jesus

[V2]
 He's worthy of glory
 And worthy of honor
 And worthy of power and all praise

[V3]
 No other name...

[V4]
 His name is exalted
 Far above the earth
 His name is high above the heavens
 His name is exalted
 Far above the earth
 Give glory and honor
 And praise unto His name

[V5]
 No other name...</lyrics>
<title>No Other Name</title>
<hymn_number>92</hymn_number>
<author>Coro Scuole David</author>
</song>